title: A Cook's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available.  The cafe recycles and composts and connects the community with local farms by also offering a CSA program and a cooking school. Menu includes vegetarian sandwiches as well vegan sandwiches (Asian tofu wrap, tempeh, and falafel), plus many different salads.
